                <li class="pure-menu-item">
                    <a href="{{ base_url }}/#" class="pure-menu-link">About</a>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="main">
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="hero-titles">
                <h2 class="hero-tagline">
                    Don't get caught with your pants down the next time
                    your email cron breaks.
                </h2>
            </div>

            <div class="marketing hero-call-to-action l-wrap pure-g">
                <div class="signup-step-1">
                    <div class="marketing-diagram content pure-u-1 u-sm-2-3 u-md-1-2">
                        <img src="{{ base_url }}/skin/images/phone-with-email.png" class="pure-img-responsive" alt="Diagram of a sample layout.">
                    </div>

                    <div class="content hero-form-wrapper pure-u-1 u-md-1-2">
                        <h3 class="marketing-header">Free Mandrill Tag Monitoring</h3>
                        <p>
                            Sign up for free below to begin receiving notifications when there
                            are any hiccups in your Mandrill delivery.  Get started <span class="highlight">in 30 seconds flat</span>.
                        </p>
                        <form class="pure-form">
                            <fieldset>
                                <a class="pure-button pure-button-primary button-start">Free Signup <i class="fa fa-arrow-right"></i> </a>
                            </fieldset>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="signup-step-2" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="marketing-diagram content pure-u-1 u-sm-2-3 u-md-1-2">
                        <img src="{{ base_url }}/skin/images/mandrill-settings.jpg" class="screenshot pure-img-responsive" alt="Diagram of a sample layout.">
                    </div>

                    <div class="content hero-form-wrapper pure-u-1 u-md-1-2">
                        <h3 class="marketing-header">Enter your Mandrill API Key</h3>
                        <p>
                            Copy your Mandrill API key from <i>Settings</i> > <i>API Keys</i>
                            and then hit <i>Save</i>.
                        </p>
                        <form class="pure-form">
                            <fieldset>
                                <input class="mandrill-api-key" type="text" placeholder="Mandrill API Key"/>
                                <a class="pure-button pure-button-primary button-check-key" href="javascript://">Check</a>
                            </fieldset>
                        </form>
                        <p>
                            <span class="status-checking" style="display: none;"><i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin"></i> Checking</span>
                            <span class="status-success" style="display: none;"><i class="fa fa-check"></i> Looks good!  Connected to Mandrill account for <span class="mandrill-username">username</span></span>
                            <span class="status-error" style="display: none;"><i class="fa fa-frown-o"></i> <span class="error-message">Error</span></span>
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="signup-step-3" style="display: none;">
                    <div class="marketing-diagram content pure-u-1 u-sm-2-3 u-md-1-2">
                        <img src="{{ base_url }}/skin/images/working.gif" class="pure-img-responsive" alt="Diagram of a sample layout.">
                    </div>

                    <div class="content hero-form-wrapper pure-u-1 u-md-1-2">
                        <h3 class="marketing-header"><i class="fa fa-cog fa-spin"></i> Just a moment</h3>
                        <p>
                            We have a whole bunch of robots typing furiously pretty much exactly
                            like Jim Carey in the illustration to the left.  Not to worry, we should be done
                            in a few seconds.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="marketing marketing-main">
            <div class="content">
                <h3 class="marketing-header">Remember the last time your email system failed?</h3>
                <p>
                    Maybe it was the cron that sends out reminder emails for your app, or maybe
                    it was the code that delivers order confirmation emails for your eCommerce store.
                </p>
                <p>
                    You didn't even realize that email had stopped going out for like 4 days, until
                    you got a call from an angry customer wondering why their shipping confirmation
                    email was taking so long to get to them.
                </p>
                <p>
                    With InsightEngine, you'll be able to rest easy knowing that your Mandrill account
                    is being proactively monitored.  InsightEngine analyzes the sending patterns of your
                    emails by tag, and if it notices a blip in sending activity, it notifies you.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Handy, right?
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="marketing how-it-works l-wrap pure-g">
            <div class="marketing-diagram content pure-u-1 u-sm-2-3 u-md-1-2">
                <img src="{{ base_url }}/skin/images/mandrill-settings.jpg" class="pure-img-responsive screenshot" alt="Diagram of a sample layout.">
            </div>

            <div class="content hero-form-wrapper pure-u-1 u-md-1-2">
                <h3 class="marketing-header">Step 1: Connect Mandrill</h3>
                <p>
                    To get started, you just need to drop your Mandrill API key
                    in.  Then we'll grab your Mandrill tags and get to work.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="marketing how-it-works l-wrap pure-g">
            <div class="marketing-diagram content pure-u-1 u-sm-2-3 u-md-1-2">
                <img src="{{ base_url }}/skin/images/manage-tags-screenshot.png" class="pure-img-responsive screenshot" alt="Diagram of a sample layout.">
            </div>

            <div class="content hero-form-wrapper pure-u-1 u-md-1-2">
                <h3 class="marketing-header">Step 2: Manage Tags</h3>
                <p>
                    Take a peek at your active Mandrill tags and feel free to
                    toggle off any that don't need to be monitored.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="marketing marketing-last how-it-works l-wrap pure-g">
            <div class="marketing-diagram content pure-u-1 u-sm-2-3 u-md-1-2">
                <img src="{{ base_url }}/skin/images/phone-with-email.png" class="pure-img-responsive" alt="Diagram of a sample layout.">
            </div>

            <div class="content hero-form-wrapper pure-u-1 u-md-1-2">
                <h3 class="marketing-header">Step 3: Get Notified</h3>
                <p>
                    If there are any issues with any of your Mandrill tags,
                    you'll get a notification email, so that you can dig
                    in and figure it out.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="legal pure-g">
                <div class="pure-u-1 u-sm-1-2">
                    <p class="legal-license">
                        This site is built with &lt;3 using Pure v0.6.0<br>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="pure-u-1 u-sm-1-2">
